Package org.vanted.plugins.layout.multilevelframework

Class SolarMerger

java.lang.Object
org.vanted.plugins.layout.multilevelframework.SolarMerger
All Implemented Interfaces:
Describable, Merger, Parameterizable
public class SolarMerger
extends Object
implements Merger
Implements the Solar Merger as described by Jürgen Hachul (but without the target edge length calculation.)
